{"tid":1504782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偽勇武？其實你地想點","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T13:11:01.000Z","uid":65526,"like":126,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"95cf90b7686859cced1472e21a428f48318279ae","tid":1504782,"uid":65526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TyDTLfm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyDTLfm.jpg&h=4d6b0e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線嘅就咁走？？<br />\n有冇搞撚柒錯啊<br />\n<br />\n背住呢位義士嘅你地對得住佢？<br />\n講好咗要救人<br />\n點解一個人都冇<br />\n<br />\n每次拉廿幾個 遲早無晒前線<br />\n成個運動真係等收皮"},{"pid":"e354a5ec8e2ed3b4d765e713762ea56cb44127f8","tid":1504782,"uid":293698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a000b417254b47081ebd8a392ab0ffb3fc9fc540","tid":1504782,"uid":257109,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"唔敢打狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c46cd878515f29a00377ba05cce3a3d42e89a60","tid":1504782,"uid":288678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6a22bf455bfdb42ca2e6dc73cf0ac8e6c13c42","tid":1504782,"uid":39010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:41:32.000Z","msg":"又唔救人 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d10cbd8e070a520f163eb441fdfca1ac1313fb8","tid":1504782,"uid":120086,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"442205dd0f3458b9473b3ad3b7f69be21df31358","tid":1504782,"uid":18473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"以後唔會去荃葵青"},{"pid":"deb5bd16567805045d4b0a3e4773e6a0155398d5","tid":1504782,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44481ef8d2e891f1bb5ad071e462756b7000c27","tid":1504782,"uid":54946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c461f2ce6da963e60e2d70c735081dea0fe48af5","tid":1504782,"uid":158008,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:55.000Z","msg":"上面幾位做乜唔上前線?"},{"pid":"52413f40aedc94630cf922e1a0b3acd4ea1c6827","tid":1504782,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,待定, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機9月6(五)搞埋</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n國泰城改左828 (三)，被炒機師空姐需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cc5dab1c1423988f357c77f0f29208f8531440","tid":1504782,"uid":158008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"KEYBOARD 勇武?"},{"pid":"9e9bd73535c99eaa8e15dccd25c3073a4cd76004","tid":1504782,"uid":100224,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>逢星期六日 1pm<br />\n你地千其唔好一齊準時入機場呀</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港身為一個國際都會，<br />\n機場就好似香港嘅心臟一樣咁重要。<br />\n每個星期都重擊心臟，香港仲有命嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警告你地班人<br />\n千其唔好逢星期六日咁準時1點一齊入機場，<br />\n大嶼山交通會負荷唔到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時塞住曬成條入機場嘅路，<br />\n搞到遊客同d crew入唔到機場，咁就慘了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇怕又要cancel好多班機⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞完星期六日，<br />\n兩日內cancel同delay左咁多班機，<br />\n又要幾日先回復到正常，<br />\n但係話咁快又到星期六日！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班仆街又出黎塞！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地知唔知機場好慘㗎？？？？？？？<br />\n未回到氣又比人再塞過！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知你地班人咁有毅力！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道左機場係春袋，<br />\n約好個個星期都準時1pm塞機場，<br />\n痴撚線！！<br />\n長遠黎講對香港經濟一定有好大影響⋯⋯<br />\n知唔知機場每秒幾多錢上落！！！<br />\n你地班廢青have no stake in the society㗎，<br />\n做一世都賺唔到咁多錢呀！<br />\n你地短短地搞兩三個星期，<br />\n到時外國政府都一定會忍唔住出聲，<br />\n令到香港政府同商家佬都好頭痕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家強烈譴責你地班暴徒阻住香港經濟發展呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安，<br />\n認同請分享！<br />\n推比全世界知！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f91b2ac3cd6c35005f24b36d225fc60f5fe9f3","tid":1504782,"uid":245201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"因為呢度唔係黃大仙。"},{"pid":"219d89a46fa4035f112a30c3c16235c332c0374e","tid":1504782,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"f305d650ee863c79a9a47f701f2dc35afa15c3e6","tid":1504782,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d9851dcfe0f43a3d5b35fb42b01f402e9db007","tid":1504782,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最慘係退嗰陣硬係有人講:停啦，前面唔夠人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬，前面就係要中後嘅人散先走到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"164da89584eabeb01c600fdc4014ac7e73a4d5d0","tid":1504782,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"大量人留守唔走係因為不嬲對峙開<br />\n<br />\n如果以後齊人就沖<br />\n我敢講以後冇唔沖既人留守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774db9ef263051efb7f305c961648dcad699a701","tid":1504782,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53219d060a8f768ac41470cf0d018f863c5026c5","tid":1504782,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"上得前線應該要有心理準備<br />\n唔係啲狗一進就退<br />\n我知好難 但如果突破唔到寧願唔好上前線<br />\n一齊入機場做和理非好過"},{"pid":"a18223491e257657ed2ac2a556c0666d450509c1","tid":1504782,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"好心酸"},{"pid":"0b04cef2e48b21c5cb2e7bfc2d5d6211fe9dc9e3","tid":1504782,"uid":186072,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:48:11.000Z","msg":"開post同屌鳩前線果啲人<br />\n你地今日有冇行過出黎上去前線睇睇發生緊咩事？<br />\n如果冇既就唔該收皮啦屌你老母<br />\n得個講字？<br />\n我夠識屌鳩你坐屋企啦<br />\n你唔勇武咪出黎做哨囉<br />\n好多人來回跑就係報緊最新資訊俾前線聽發生緊咩事<br />\n你就坐係到睇直播望住個tg group黎屌<br />\n咁中意屌咪落去前線屌鳩人做